org.myrobotlab.framework.repo

Class ServiceType

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.myrobotlab.framework.repo.ServiceType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.util.Comparator<ServiceType>

    public class ServiceType
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, java.util.Comparator<ServiceType>
    list of relations from a Service type to a Dependency key the key is used to look up in the masterList - this keeps the data normalized and if one Service fulfills its dependency and the dependency is shared with another Service type, it is fulfilled there too The dependency key is the "org" - no version is keyed at the moment.. this would be something to avoid anyway (complexities of cross-versions - jar hell)
